{"id":23031,"date":"2024-01-01T06:34:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-01T01:04:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=23031"},"modified":"2023-02-02T13:57:20","modified_gmt":"2023-02-02T08:27:20","slug":"spa-bathroom-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/spa-bathroom-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"A Zen-Like Spa Bathroom In Your Home? Here\u2019s How You Can Get One"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Spa bathroom ideas for a soothing escape and any-time pampering right in your home<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The difference between a regular bathroom and a spa bathroom is you will never want to leave the latter. When it comes to home improvement and design, one immediately thinks of the living room or bedroom and rarely about the bathroom. Since the bathroom is mainly considered for its utility, its design remains functional. But you can turn this area into your own personal oasis by recreating a spa room design in your bathroom.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We know this has got you wondering about how to make your apartment bathroom look like a spa. Well, fret not, because we have the best ideas for you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get The Spa Bathroom Essentials Right<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You don\u2019t have to necessarily do over your entire bathroom to turn it into an at-home spa. You can make a few changes to your existing bathroom to make it feel like your very own personal spa. Begin by making some small investments in spa essentials like luxe hand and bath towels. Do away with the many different bottles and containers and get trendy dispensers instead. Transfer your soaps, shampoos, lotions and conditioners into designer dispensers. This will give your bathroom a uniform and personalised look instead of appearing cluttered with different branded packaging.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183014\/bathroom-home-spa-idea.jpg\" alt=\"opt for right spa bathroom essentials\" class=\"wp-image-23032\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183014\/bathroom-home-spa-idea.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183014\/bathroom-home-spa-idea-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183014\/bathroom-home-spa-idea-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183014\/bathroom-home-spa-idea-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Get trendy towels and dispensers for your bathroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Accessories And Storage Hacks For Your Spa Bathroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re confused about how to make a small bathroom look like a spa, we suggest switching to smart storage solutions. Eliminate all the clutter to turn your bathroom into a space that feels calm and relaxing. Install sleek cabinets and drawers under the basin to free up the vanity area. Minimalist glass wall shelves help keep your bathroom essentials well-organised while looking stylish. Cane baskets are a great way to store fresh towels in your spa bathroom. Once you\u2019ve put away the clutter, accessorise the space with natural decor elements like house plants, river stones, pebbles and scented candles.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183030\/small-spa-bathroom-with-accessories-hacks.jpg\" alt=\"A small bathroom ideas with natural decor elements brings a calm and relaxing vibe.\" class=\"wp-image-23035\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183030\/small-spa-bathroom-with-accessories-hacks.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183030\/small-spa-bathroom-with-accessories-hacks-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183030\/small-spa-bathroom-with-accessories-hacks-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183030\/small-spa-bathroom-with-accessories-hacks-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Keep fresh towels in cane baskets for a neat look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-storage-ideas\/\">Bathroom Storage Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Get A Luxurious Spa In A Small Bathroom With Gold-Finish Fixtures<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Up the luxury quotient of your small bathroom by adding a touch of gold to your existing bathroom interiors. Install bathroom faucets, cabinet handles, and door handles in a gold finish instead of going for something regular. It looks particularly great when set against white. In this green-and-white-themed bathroom, the golden fixtures and handles subtly enhance the sophistication. The white dispensers blend in well with the rest of the bathroom and let the gold do all the talking. The designer mirror with a geometric frame in golden completes the look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183025\/luxury-home-spa-bathroom-with-gold-finish-fixtures.jpg\" alt=\"A luxury green and white bathroom with spa-like appeal with gold-finish fixtures\" class=\"wp-image-23034\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183025\/luxury-home-spa-bathroom-with-gold-finish-fixtures.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183025\/luxury-home-spa-bathroom-with-gold-finish-fixtures-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183025\/luxury-home-spa-bathroom-with-gold-finish-fixtures-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/25183025\/luxury-home-spa-bathroom-with-gold-finish-fixtures-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Faucets in an elegant gold finish define luxury<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Invest In A Classy Rain Shower Head For Your Spa Bathroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For the ultimate spa experience at home, you will want to do away with your regular shower head and get a rain shower head instead. This is one of the best small spa bathroom ideas that can completely transform the feel of your bathroom space. A rain shower does a fabulous job of relaxing tense muscles, and you won\u2019t feel the need to book an appointment at your favourite spa again. By enclosing the shower area with a glass door or partition, you can also turn it into a mini steam room. Check out this elegant bathroom with a glass door partition for the shower area. It also features vertical open shelving to make room for scented candles that can totally elevate your shower experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112622\/spa-style-bathroom-with-shower-head.jpg\" alt=\"The bathroom in the spa style features a luxurious shower head that provides a soothing and rejuvenating water flow\" class=\"wp-image-42053\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112622\/spa-style-bathroom-with-shower-head.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112622\/spa-style-bathroom-with-shower-head-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112622\/spa-style-bathroom-with-shower-head-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112622\/spa-style-bathroom-with-shower-head-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A good rain shower head is a must-have<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Remodelling The Entire Bathroom To Turn It Into A Spa Bathroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re planning to remodel your entire bathroom with a spa room design, you have the opportunity to pick colours and patterns that lend a spa-like feeling to your bathroom. Colours have the most significant impact on the ambience of your bathroom. So when you want to make your bathroom look like a spa, start with softer hues like white, cream, and beige to infuse a sense of lightness into the space. Pick a colour and use it throughout the bathroom \u2014 be it the tiles, the paint, the cabinets, or the wallpaper. This bathroom in a soothing cream colour with white bath fixtures and concealed LED strip lights gives a glowing effect. We love the minimal shelving on the walls to create a clean and pristine spa bathroom look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112628\/turn-bathroom-design-into-spa.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom design with colours and patterns offer a calm spa-like vibe\" class=\"wp-image-42054\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112628\/turn-bathroom-design-into-spa.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112628\/turn-bathroom-design-into-spa-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112628\/turn-bathroom-design-into-spa-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112628\/turn-bathroom-design-into-spa-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Light colours offer a calm spa-like vibe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Turn Your Small Bathroom Into A Designer Bathroom Spa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Just because you are falling short of space does not mean you keep yourself away from some in-house spa time! This spa idea for small bathrooms gives your bathroom a designer touch while being easy on the pocket. When you want to make your bathroom look like a spa on a budget, opt for a waterproof wallpaper. This bathroom features a beautiful thin stripe wallpaper in warm colours which gives it an inviting ambience. A pristine white washbasin is a beautiful addition to this spa bathroom with the bathtub giving it the quintessential spa feel. Light some fragrant candles and soak the stress away.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112612\/small-spa-like-bathroom-with-wallpaper.jpg\" alt=\"Transform your small bathroom into a stylish and functional space with our selection of waterproof wallpaper\" class=\"wp-image-42051\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112612\/small-spa-like-bathroom-with-wallpaper.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112612\/small-spa-like-bathroom-with-wallpaper-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112612\/small-spa-like-bathroom-with-wallpaper-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/01112612\/small-spa-like-bathroom-with-wallpaper-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Waterproof wallpapers are a budget-friendly option<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With your own spa bathroom, you won\u2019t have to worry about booking appointments or waitlists at your favourite spa. On a stressful or rough day, simply pop into your bathroom for anytime relaxation and rejuvenation session from the comfort of your home. Whether you want to make significant changes or small ones, these home spa ideas are easy ways to introduce spa room design to your bathroom. Want expert help in creating the perfect bathroom spa ambience in your home? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">Book a free consultation<\/a> with our experienced designers today!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-renovation-ideas\/\">Bathroom Renovation Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/luxury-bathroom-design\/\">Luxury Bathroom Design<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Design your personal oasis of comfort<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"i